	<div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="https://dealbook.nytimes.com/2014/10/31/morning-agenda-citigroups-about-face/" data-title="Morning Agenda: Citigroup&#8217;s About-Face" data-description="Citigroup says it has to cut its third-quarter profit by $600 million because of legal expenses. | Apple chief&#039;s coming out. | Judge approves bankruptcy plan for Stockton, Calif.">
